s/kelley07.pdf|accessdate=12 May 2008| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318120640/http://www.ccc.nps.navy.mil/research/theses/kelley07.pdf| archivedate=18 March 2009}}</ref>\n<ref name=NHH>{{cite book|last=Peniston|first=Bradley|title=No Higher Honor: Saving the USS Samuel B. Roberts in the Persian Gulf| publisher=United States Naval Institute Press|date=July 2006|isbn=1-59114-661-5}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NYT somalia step\">{{cite news|title=A Big Second Step in Somalia|work=New York Times|date=4 May 1993}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Gup 2000\">The Book of Honor: Cover Lives and Classified Deaths at the CIA by Ted Gup, 2000</ref>\n<ref name=NYTttt>{{cite news|title=Two Tough Tracks in Somalia|work=New York Times|date=10 December 1992}}</ref>\n<ref name=BHD>{{cite book|last=Bowden|first=Mark|authorlink=Mark Bowden|title=Black Hawk Down: A Story of Modern War|publisher=Signet|year=2001|isbn=0-451-20393-3|url=https://archive.org/details/blackhawkdownsto00bowd_0}}</ref><ref name=BoG>\n{{cite book|last=Eversmann|first=Matt|first2=Dan |last2=Schilling |title=The Battle of Mogadishu: Firsthand Accounts from the Men of Task Force Ranger|publisher=Presidio Press|date=July 2006|isbn=0-345-46668-3}}</ref>\n<ref name=Kozaryn>{{cite news|last=D. Kozaryn|first=Linda|title=U.S. Special Operations Forces Change \"Face of War\"|work=American Forces Press Service|date=14 December 2001}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"reach of war\">{{cite news |first =Eric Schmitt |last =Thom Shanker |title =The Reach of War: Military; Special Warriors Have Growing Ranks and Growing Pains in Taking Key Antiterror Role |url =https://www.nytimes.com/2004/08/02/world/reach-war-military-special-warriors-have-growing-ranks-growing-pains-taking-key.html |work =The New York Times |date =2 August 2004 |accessdate =11 March 2008 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20101027173816/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/08/02/world/reach-war-military-special-warriors-have-growing-ranks-growing-pains-taking-key.html |archive-dat