rt of, special operations. Some notable recipients include;\n*[[Lieutenant General (United States)|Lieutenant General]] [[Samuel V. Wilson]]\n*[[Colonel]] [[Ralph Puckett]]\n*[[SCPO]] [[Kristin Beck]]\n*[[Lieutenant colonel (United States)|LTC]] [[William Carnall]]\n\nSince it was created, there have been more than 50 recipients, only five of whom were not American, including;\n*[[General]] [[Beno\u00eet Puga]] (France)\n*[[Captain (armed forces)|Kaptein]] [[Gunnar S\u00f8nsteby]], 2008 (Norway)<ref name=\"Jensen\">Jensen, Finn Robert; Gunnar \"Kjakan\" S\u00f8nsteby Om samhold og innsatsvilje; Pantagruel forlag; Oslo; 2008</ref>\n*\u2020 [[Genera\u0142 broni]] [[W\u0142odzimierz Potasi\u0144ski]], 2010 (Poland)<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20121209185746/http://www.shadowspear.com/vb/threads/united-states-special-operations-command-medal-to-lt-gen-w%C5%82odzimierz-potasi%C5%84ski.6197/ USSOCOM Medal recipients]</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wojskaspecjalne.mil.pl/45,more,129-ussocom_commander_visits_polsocom.html?ln=en |title=NEWS &#124; USSOCOM Commander visits POLSOCOM &#124; Dow\u00f3dztwo Wojsk Specjalnych |publisher=Wojskaspecjalne.mil.pl |date=2010-05-14 |accessdate=2013-04-22 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120805211914/http://www.wojskaspecjalne.mil.pl/45,more,129-ussocom_commander_visits_polsocom.html?ln=en |archive-date=5 August 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref> \n*[[Genera\u0142 dywizji]] [[Piotr Patalong]], 2014 (Poland)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mon.gov.pl/aktualnosci/artykul/najnowsze/2014-10-29-medal-dowodztwa-operacji-specjalnych-usa-dla-polskiego-generala/ |title=Medal USSOCOM dla polskiego genera\u0142a |publisher=mon.gov.pl |date=2014-10-29 |accessdate=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029164646/http://mon.gov.pl/aktualnosci/artykul/najnowsze/2014-10-29-medal-dowodztwa-operacji-specjalnych-usa-dla-polskiego-generala/ |archive-date=29 October 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n*[[Genera\u0142 brygady]] [[Jerzy Gut]], 2014 (Poland)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wojsko-polskie.pl/pl/z-zycia-wojska/30655,amerykanskie-dowodztwo-operacji-specjalnych-docenilo-polskiego-generala.html |title=Ameryka\u0144skie Dow\u00f3dztwo Operacji Specjalnych doceni\u0142o polskiego genera\u0142a |publisher=wojsko-polskie.l |date=2014-06-03 |accessdate=2014-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606204407/http://www.wojsko-polskie.pl/pl/z-zycia-wojska/30655,amerykanskie-dowodztwo-operacji-specjalnych-docenilo-polskiego-generala.html |archive-date=6 June 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n:(\u2020 [[wikt:posthumous|posthumously]])\n\n==References==\n\n===Citations===\n{{Reflist|30em|refs=\n<ref name=\"2015 SOCOM Fact book\">{{cite book |author=SOCOM Public Affairs |title=SOCOM Fact Book 2015 |url=http://www.socom.mil/Documents/2015_Fact_Book.pdf |year=2015 |publisher=SOCOM Public Affairs }}{{Dead link|date=May 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"2013 SOCOM Fact book\">{{cite book|author=SOCOM Public Affairs|title=SOCOM Fact Book 2013|url=http://www.socom.mil/News/Documents/USSOCOM_Fact_Book_2013.pdf|year=2013|publisher=SOCOM Public Affairs|access-date=14 February 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130214222055/http://www.socom.mil/News/Documents/USSOCOM_Fact_Book_2013.pdf|archive-date=14 February 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NYT Regime thought\">{{cite news|first=Thom|last=Shanker|title=Regime Thought War Unlikely, Iraqis Tell U.S|work=The New York Times|date=12 February 2004}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NYT Bang Panama\">{{cite news|first=Larry|last=Rother|title=With a Bang, Panama Is Erasing House of Horrors|work=The New York Times|date=6 December 1996}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Adm Holloway bio\">{{cite web|title=Biography of Admiral James L. Holloway III, US Navy (Ret.)|date=June 2006|url=http://www.history.navy.mil/bios/holloway_j.htm|accessdate=21 March 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090825040049/http://www.hist